39:14.617 --> 39:17.920
<i>♪ Faithful Yeah ♪</i>

39:19.723 --> 39:22.825
You know, now I see
why David had the blueprints.

39:22.827 --> 39:24.526
This is serious.
Very.

39:24.528 --> 39:27.930
They even come
from the Vineyard for this.

39:28.598 --> 39:33.802
Now, this is Megan Weeks,
last year's winner.

39:33.804 --> 39:36.772
Gee, Megan, what a lovely entry.

39:36.774 --> 39:39.908
I was thinking of
adding another victim.

39:39.910 --> 39:42.077
Ah-hah.

39:42.079 --> 39:43.746
Charming.

39:43.748 --> 39:46.482
[BOTH CHUCKLE]

39:47.917 --> 39:51.120
Oh, my God!

39:51.122 --> 39:53.622
You madman!

39:53.624 --> 39:57.960
Oh, tread softly, sweet
