39:57.962 --> 39:59.428
Wow!

40:00.063 --> 40:03.532
Esther, kiss the king!

40:03.767 --> 40:08.470
Oh, I take it all back.
This is amazing.

40:08.472 --> 40:12.574
I take it all back.
You're a genius.

40:12.576 --> 40:13.008
Thank you.

40:13.010 --> 40:14.743
PAUL:
Hey, what about me? I helped.

40:14.745 --> 40:18.714
You want credit? Last night I'm
nuts, now you want credit?

40:18.716 --> 40:20.582
I provided moral support.

40:20.584 --> 40:21.483
Hey.

40:21.485 --> 40:23.552
This is really cool.

40:23.554 --> 40:25.120
You may breastfeed the king.

40:25.122 --> 40:27.923
And should there
be any leftovers...
Paul!

40:27.925 --> 40:28.857
What?
Eww.

40:28.859 --> 40:33.762
<b>♪ ["THIS IS HOW WE DO IT" BY ♪
♪ MONTELL JORDAN PLAYS] ♪</b>

40:37.867 --> 40:40.169
We got 'em, see?
They're looking.

40:40.171 --> 40:41.069
Who's looking?

40:41.071 --> 40:45.107
Boys. Men. Ignore 'em.

40:45.109 --> 40:45.774
More hip.

40:45.776 --> 40:48.811
God, this thing is killing me.
My breasts hurt.

40:48.813 --> 40:51.480
Just own the beach, Rachel.
Can you do that?

40:51.482 --> 40:55.150
Walk cool.
Own the beach.

40:55.152 --> 40:56.919
Hi.

40:56.921 --> 40:59.488
The judging is over.
You're free.

40:59.490 --> 41:01.089
Oh, thank God.

41:01.091 --> 41:03.525
Arise, arise, my liege.

41:04.861 --> 41:06.562
Gimme your hand.

41:06.763 --> 41:09.531
They'll announce in 10 minutes.

41:10.166 --> 41:12.601
Let me get you a towel.
You okay?

41:12.603 --> 41:14.536
Too much sun, maybe.
Hang on.

41:14.538 --> 41:16.472
Plus being buried.

41:16.474 --> 41:18.173
I'm a little light-headed.

41:18.175 --> 41:19.175
Sure.

41:19.176 --> 41:23.545
You know, maybe it's just thrill
of the competition, huh?

41:26.850 --> 41:28.217
Excuse me.

41:32.155 --> 41:33.822
What are you lookin' at?

41:33.824 --> 41:37.226
An act of God. Two acts.

41:37.228 --> 41:39.094
Turn around, you sweet things.

41:39.096 --> 41:40.996
Look at that.

41:40.998 --> 41:42.631
Junior Mints.

41:47.237 --> 41:48.737
Oops.

41:52.075 --> 41:55.077
Rachel! Rachel!

41:55.079 --> 41:55.811
Hi, Daddy.

41:55.813 --> 41:56.879
Never mind 'Hi, Daddy'.

41:56.881 --> 41:59.681
What are you doing?
You're practically naked!

41:59.683 --> 42:00.582
I'm making you decent.

42:00.584 --> 42:01.917
I'm wearing a bathing suit.

42:01.919 --> 42:04.553
Go away. Please leave the
premises. You!

42:04.555 --> 42:05.220
Hi.

42:05.222 --> 42:07.689
Put that towel on!
Put that on!

42:07.691 --> 42:09.791
We're on a beach!

42:09.793 --> 42:11.093
Cindy, it's okay.

42:11.095 --> 42:13.896
You're perfect,
I want you to know that.

42:13.898 --> 42:15.097
Don't you look at me.

42:15.099 --> 42:17.065
You're being ridiculous.

42:17.067 --> 42:19.535
What got into you?

42:20.770 --> 42:22.638
Dad, what's the matter?

42:23.573 --> 42:25.240
Dad, what?

42:29.045 --> 42:30.913
Gillian?

42:30.915 --> 42:31.947
Dad?

42:31.949 --> 42:34.149
Gillian!

42:34.151 --> 42:36.552
Daddy! Daddy!

42:42.191 --> 42:46.061
Wake up. Come on.
Come on, hey, wake up.

42:46.063 --> 42:48.230
Open your eyes. Come on.

42:48.798 --> 42:51.700
Come on. There you go.

42:55.672 --> 42:58.307
You thought you saw Gillian.

43:01.844 --> 43:03.278
Daddy, are you all right?

43:03.280 --> 43:04.112
Yeah.

43:04.114 --> 43:06.081
I'm fine.
He's okay.

43:06.215 --> 43:08.850
Too much sun. He'll be fine.

43:11.120 --> 43:12.187
You won.

43:12.189 --> 43:14.623
Hey! You won, you won!

43:14.625 --> 43:16.325
Can we just have a little room?

43:16.327 --> 43:17.726
Back up. Give him some air.

43:17.728 --> 43:21.630
Megan Weeks is crushed.
Her life is ruined.

43:22.231 --> 43:24.066
Come on, Rache, he's fine.

43:24.068 --> 43:26.668
He's not fine.
He thought he saw her.

43:26.670 --> 43:29.705
Maybe it was your bathing suit
that made him faint.

43:29.707 --> 43:32.240
Speaking of which, this is
cutting off circulation.

43:32.242 --> 43:35.177
It's lucky I don't pass out.

43:38.214 --> 43:40.182
He screamed her name.

43:41.384 --> 43:44.019
[HORN HONKS]

43:46.923 --> 43:47.923
Hey.
Hi.

43:47.925 --> 43:53.295
There's this party tonight.
Supposed to be good.

43:54.130 --> 43:56.031
Wanna go?

43:57.200 --> 43:59.735
With you?

43:59.737 --> 44:01.169
Yeah.

44:05.675 --> 44:07.209
Okay, sure.

44:07.211 --> 44:09.945
I'll get somebody
for you if you want.

44:09.947 --> 44:14.683
I know how to snap my finger,
thank you very much.

44:18.888 --> 44:20.222
I'll pick you up.

44:20.224 --> 44:23.925
Eight thirty.
Great.

44:26.195 --> 44:28.296
[STARTS CAR]

44:31.100 --> 44:32.701
I have a date!

44:32.703 --> 44:34.102
Yeah, I see.

44:34.104 --> 44:35.737
Tonight!

44:35.739 --> 44:37.272
I caught that too.

45:29.726 --> 45:33.028
So, what's with the meditation?

45:33.030 --> 45:35.464
I have a date.

45:36.966 --> 45:40.102
Dates scare me.

45:41.471 --> 45:42.471
Yeah, me too.

45:42.473 --> 45:47.375
You must have been nervous
getting off that ferry.

45:48.377 --> 45:53.849
It was probably more terrifying
getting on the ferry.

45:54.484 --> 45:58.086
By the time it docked, I'd...

45:58.287 --> 46:03.058
Well, I-I wasn't nervous.

46:03.060 --> 46:05.127
Why?

46:06.028 --> 46:08.363
I don't know, really.

46:08.998 --> 46:11.867
This might surprise you,

46:11.869 --> 46:16.805
but I was hoping
you and my father...

46:18.141 --> 46:19.508
You don't even know me.

46:19.510 --> 46:23.512
Well, you seem to
be on this planet.

46:44.901 --> 46:46.301
[BIRDS CALLING]

47:01.484 --> 47:02.951
You're gonna scare the fish.

47:02.953 --> 47:06.521
I'm sure what you're doing
puts them at ease.

47:09.158 --> 47:11.026
Feeling better?

47:11.028 --> 47:12.594
Much.

47:13.529 --> 47:15.297
Great.

47:16.132 --> 47:19.067
David, we got a problem.

47:19.069 --> 47:21.369
Esther's worried
about Rachel living with you.

47:21.371 --> 47:23.505
How many times
are we gonna play that record?

47:23.507 --> 47:24.940
It's gone beyond talk now.

47:24.942 --> 47:27.976
She's got an appointment
with a judge on Monday,

47:27.978 --> 47:31.446
and I think she might
move for custody or something.

47:31.448 --> 47:32.214
What?

47:32.216 --> 47:36.218
I didn't know this was coming,
I swear it.

47:36.220 --> 47:37.485
She's going to court?

47:37.487 --> 47:40.188
She doesn't want to, and I'm
sure it won't come to that.

47:40.190 --> 47:43.325
I am telling you
so you can help yourself.

47:43.327 --> 47:45.260
You've got to act normal...

47:45.262 --> 47:46.962
you know,
use a napkin at dinner,

47:46.964 --> 47:48.997
try to breathe
between sentences.

47:48.999 --> 47:52.334
If you see Gillian again,
wave subtle.

47:52.336 --> 47:55.437
PAUL:
David, this is
dangerous and illegal.

47:55.439 --> 47:56.938
It's also very upsetting to me.

47:56.940 --> 48:00.642
I have a problem with high
speed. The speed concerns me.

48:00.644 --> 48:02.010
DAVID:
Then shut your eyes.

48:02.012 --> 48:04.145
I told you what I
told you in confidence.

48:04.147 --> 48:06.548
I hope you're not
gonna barge in there...

48:06.550 --> 48:08.383
Esther's planning to take my kid

48:08.385 --> 48:10.285
and I'm supposed to
keep my mouth shut.

48:10.287 --> 48:13.288
Broach it to her naturally so
she doesn't know I ratted.

48:13.290 --> 48:16.591
'How are you? Nice dress.
Make any court dates?'

48:16.593 --> 48:18.326
Shut up!

48:18.594 --> 48:22.197
That was very helpful.
Slow down, please.

48:22.199 --> 48:24.332
Watch it! Jesus!

48:24.934 --> 48:27.235
Just let me out of the car
right here. This is fine.

48:27.237 --> 48:30.205
And you keep
going into the trees.

48:43.419 --> 48:47.088
Esther, a moment of
your time, please.

48:47.090 --> 48:48.323
What's wrong?

48:48.325 --> 48:50.926
I need a moment.
Can I have a moment?

48:50.928 --> 48:52.294
Certainly.

48:53.329 --> 48:54.696
Excuse me.

49:02.104 --> 49:05.140
You come here under the guise
of a vacation weekend,

49:05.142 --> 49:08.443
and you have...
you plan to see a judge!

49:08.445 --> 49:10.278
It's like what?
Calm down.

49:10.280 --> 49:12.514
You're punishing me
for hurting too much.

49:12.516 --> 49:13.481
I shouldn't hurt anymore.

49:13.483 --> 49:16.451
The fucking statute of
limitations on pain has run out!

49:16.453 --> 49:18.086
Let me tell you why I feel...

49:18.088 --> 49:19.220
Does Rachel know?

49:19.222 --> 49:20.956
No. She would never
choose to leave you.

49:20.958 --> 49:22.324
I'm doing it in
her best interests.

49:22.326 --> 49:26.161
Rip her from her father! That's
her best fucking interest!

49:26.163 --> 49:27.562
Do you want
an adult conversation,

49:27.564 --> 49:29.597
or see how many
times you can swear?

49:29.599 --> 49:30.632
Fuck you. How many's that?

49:30.634 --> 49:34.502
I was on that boat too.
You have no priority on this.

49:34.504 --> 49:36.037
My priority is my daughter.

49:36.039 --> 49:37.372
Then make her one!

49:37.374 --> 49:39.374
I want you to get
out of the house!

49:39.376 --> 49:41.042
I'm sick of you
barging into my life.

49:41.044 --> 49:45.213
If I hadn't barged in, you
wouldn't have a life, David!

49:45.215 --> 49:47.615
I'm the one who
found you, remember?

49:47.617 --> 49:51.686
I'm the one who barged in after
you gobbled the sleeping pills.

49:51.688 --> 49:54.622
Let's not forget
that little trivia.

50:01.497 --> 50:04.099
Took me a long time
to like you, David.

50:04.101 --> 50:08.136
It's taken me even longer to
care, but I do care now.

50:08.304 --> 50:10.472
If you want to throw your life
down the toilet,

50:10.474 --> 50:14.275
I will cry for you
whether you believe it or not.

50:14.277 --> 50:19.347
But if you think that I'd let
you take Rachel down with you...

50:20.649 --> 50:23.051
then you don't know who I am.

50:23.053 --> 50:28.223
You've never made the slightest
effort to know who I am.

50:58.354 --> 51:00.288
Hi.
Hi.

51:11.167 --> 51:13.435
All set.
Ready?

51:18.541 --> 51:20.075
See you later, Daddy. Bye.

51:20.077 --> 51:21.209
Where you goin'?

51:21.211 --> 51:22.410
Oh, I-I have a date.

51:22.412 --> 51:24.746
Didn't I tell you?
I-I thought I did. Funny.

51:24.748 --> 51:29.184
Daddy, you remember Joey.
Joey, my father. Daddy, Joey.

51:29.186 --> 51:30.118
All right. Bye.

51:30.120 --> 51:31.619
Wait. You're going out
with him?

51:31.621 --> 51:34.522
Yeah, we won't be
too late. See you.

51:34.524 --> 51:36.357
Hold it.

51:38.260 --> 51:39.861
Do you take drugs?

51:39.863 --> 51:41.329
No.

51:41.464 --> 51:44.265
How many holes do you have
in your ears?

51:44.267 --> 51:45.733
Nose?
Six.

51:45.735 --> 51:46.634
Three. Four.

51:46.636 --> 51:50.338
'Night! 'Night!
'Night, 'night, 'night.

51:56.879 --> 51:58.813
I'm gonna skip dinner.

51:59.815 --> 52:01.416
Take a walk.

52:05.721 --> 52:08.690
[♪♪♪]

52:11.627 --> 52:15.163
[DISTANT BELL TOLLING]

52:27.510 --> 52:29.644
Remember the meteor shower?

52:30.446 --> 52:34.249
A certain daughter was conceived
under those stars.

52:34.884 --> 52:38.153
I thought I saw you
on the beach today.

52:38.155 --> 52:40.522
It wasn't you, was it?

52:40.524 --> 52:42.190
No.

52:42.324 --> 52:44.392
I must have been hallucinating.

52:44.394 --> 52:47.762
It was different from the way
I see you here.

52:48.230 --> 52:50.398
Who knows?
Maybe they're right.

52:50.400 --> 52:54.402
I am sitting on a rock,
talking to a ghost.

52:58.207 --> 52:59.874
I could go.

52:59.876 --> 53:01.409
No.

53:05.848 --> 53:08.550
I think I am in trouble.

53:09.385 --> 53:10.752
A little.

53:12.788 --> 53:14.255
Why?

53:14.423 --> 53:16.558
I think maybe I'm sick.

53:18.494 --> 53:20.461
I pretend I'm okay.

53:22.965 --> 53:24.465
Am I sick?

53:26.502 --> 53:29.337
I always hated good dreams.

53:30.739 --> 53:34.309
I-I couldn't take the
disappointment of waking up.

53:34.843 --> 53:39.414
And then I figured out a way to
know whether I was dreaming.

53:40.883 --> 53:42.550
What are you talking about?

53:42.552 --> 53:44.886
I realized that in
most of my dreams

53:44.888 --> 53:47.488
I'd ask myself,
'Am I dreaming?'

53:47.490 --> 53:50.325
I'd never ask that
when I was awake.

53:51.227 --> 53:52.694
So I finally figured it out.

53:52.696 --> 53:56.364
If I ever wondered,
is this a dream or not,

53:56.366 --> 53:58.299
then I knew it was.

54:00.736 --> 54:02.403
You ever wonder?

54:05.908 --> 54:08.243
Don't leave.

54:09.712 --> 54:11.512
I'm not leaving.

54:17.286 --> 54:19.587
[CHATTERING]
[♪♪♪]

54:31.267 --> 54:32.634
Joey!

54:36.505 --> 54:38.039
Hey, hey, Joey.

54:38.041 --> 54:39.474
Danny.

54:39.476 --> 54:40.541
Rachel.

54:40.543 --> 54:41.676
Hi.
Hi.

54:41.678 --> 54:46.648
Have some punch. It's a vintage
batch I made myself.

54:49.852 --> 54:50.852
Yuck.

54:50.854 --> 54:52.587
It's a zombie.

54:52.589 --> 54:54.355
What's in a zombie?

54:54.357 --> 54:57.292
Rum and stuff.
It's good.

54:59.628 --> 55:01.696
I'll get some more.

55:06.568 --> 55:09.437
Would you try talking to him?

55:09.772 --> 55:11.572
You could be an objective voice.

55:11.574 --> 55:14.609
It seems no matter
what I say, he just...

55:14.611 --> 55:17.845
Maybe if you
weren't so shy about it.

55:17.980 --> 55:21.683
This isn't
something I want to do.

55:21.685 --> 55:23.017
Then don't.

55:23.019 --> 55:25.353
A man shouldn't
lose his daughter

55:25.355 --> 55:26.954
for taking long
walks on the beach.

55:26.956 --> 55:28.856
It isn't just that.

55:28.858 --> 55:30.892
Then what is it?

55:30.894 --> 55:34.595
Is there something else
you're not telling me?

55:35.931 --> 55:37.398
No.

55:37.700 --> 55:39.867
Then I don't see his crime.

55:39.869 --> 55:43.404
His wife is dead, and he doesn't
want to let her go.

55:44.340 --> 55:47.108
My husband let me go
while I was still living.

55:47.110 --> 55:50.411
I'd prefer to
think he was crazy.

55:51.647 --> 55:54.482
If you could just talk to him.

55:55.417 --> 55:59.120
<b>♪ ['AFTER THE LOVIN' BY ENGELBERT ♪
♪ HUMPERDINCK PLAYS] ♪</b>

56:03.425 --> 56:05.626
<i>♪ And I hope you can hear ♪</i>

56:05.628 --> 56:11.699
<i>♪ What the words</i>
<i>and the music have to say ♪</i>

56:15.137 --> 56:18.406
<i>♪ It's so hard to explain ♪</i>

56:18.408 --> 56:21.476
<i>♪ Everything that I'm feeling ♪</i>

56:21.478 --> 56:27.415
<i>♪ Face-to-face,</i>
<i>I just seem to go dry ♪</i>

56:27.716 --> 56:30.485
<i>♪ But I love you so much ♪</i>

56:30.487 --> 56:33.421
<i>♪ That the sound... ♪</i>
[LAUGHS]

56:36.692 --> 56:41.429
You know, I-I didn't get a
chance to sing my encore, so...

56:42.097 --> 56:43.498
Where is everybody?

56:43.500 --> 56:46.501
Well, uh,
Rachel went out on a date.

56:46.503 --> 56:49.137
David ran away from home.

56:49.139 --> 56:51.472
Kevin and Esther
went looking for him.

56:51.474 --> 56:58.079
So that leaves just you, me,
and the moonlight.

56:59.014 --> 57:01.649
Come on, let me inspect you
for tonsillitis.

57:01.651 --> 57:04.919
Have you been
pathetic your entire life?

57:04.921 --> 57:06.621
Uh, not yet.

57:06.623 --> 57:10.491
Come on, don't look at me like
that. You enjoy this banter.

57:10.493 --> 57:12.994
The bathing suits, the outfits,

57:12.996 --> 57:14.962
the hormone 'I am woman' strut.

57:14.964 --> 57:18.599
But don't worry, you're safe.
I'm married to Esther.

57:18.601 --> 57:22.470
No, no, I'm safe,
'cause men like you

57:22.472 --> 57:26.607
never do anything
except sit on porches

57:26.609 --> 57:29.877
and watch things and say things,

57:29.879 --> 57:32.547
but never do things.

57:32.549 --> 57:34.115
You think so, huh?

57:37.820 --> 57:40.121
You wanna kiss me?

57:41.657 --> 57:43.524
I beg your pardon?

57:46.462 --> 57:48.729
We've been doing
this flirting thing,

57:48.731 --> 57:51.132
and you've been staring at me
since you got here.

57:51.134 --> 57:54.802
You were practically
drooling at the beach.

57:56.238 --> 57:59.807
I'm sure you
must have thought...

58:00.609 --> 58:03.177
what it would be like.

58:11.920 --> 58:14.222
Maybe we should just see.

58:18.527 --> 58:21.028
Maybe you should just...

58:22.631 --> 58:26.133
I don't know...
touch me a little.

58:32.708 --> 58:34.141
Take a chance.

58:36.712 --> 58:38.613
Nobody has to know.

58:44.052 --> 58:45.820
See?

