01:00:57.352 --> 01:00:58.786
What?

01:00:58.788 --> 01:00:59.788
A truck, Esther.

01:00:59.789 --> 01:01:01.288
If life were like
a goddamn truck,

01:01:01.290 --> 01:01:04.158
better to get run
over or passed over?

01:01:05.060 --> 01:01:08.062
You're standing by
the side of the road?

01:01:08.897 --> 01:01:10.164
Yeah.

01:01:10.298 --> 01:01:13.034
