01:01:14.036 --> 01:01:17.972
It's a big joke, right?
Just forget it, all right?

01:01:17.974 --> 01:01:21.242
Forget it. Forget it.
It's fine, really.

01:01:22.711 --> 01:01:24.445
If life were like a truck.

01:01:27.349 --> 01:01:28.983
I'm fine.
