What kind of a daydream is that?

01:05:04.433 --> 01:05:05.266
That was sunstroke.

01:05:05.268 --> 01:05:07.968
David, don't you
see what you're doing?

01:05:07.970 --> 01:05:09.670
You're trying to
deny she's gone.

01:05:09.672 --> 01:05:12.339
