01:05:57.954 --> 01:06:01.689
David, you can't
keep living in a fantasy.

01:06:01.691 --> 01:06:04.658
Yes, it's a fantasy!
It's a fantasy!

01:06:04.660 --> 01:06:06.293
How many normal, married people,

01:06:06.295 --> 01:06:07.628
while making love
to their spouse,

01:06:07.630 --> 01:06:10.464
