01:10:02.631 --> 01:10:06.433
You're old, Mom.
Give it up.

01:10:06.435 --> 01:10:07.901
Funny.

01:10:08.469 --> 01:10:10.737
Who's passing who now?

01:10:10.739 --> 01:10:13.407
