01:10:50.512 --> 01:10:52.579
Mommy, she was here.
No, she was here.

01:10:52.581 --> 01:10:55.983
It's okay, Rache.
It's okay. It's okay.

01:10:56.951 --> 01:10:59.953
It was just a dream.
It was a dream.

01:10:59.955 --> 01:11:01.355
Mommy was here.

01:11:01.357 --> 01:11:03.323
