01:11:03.325 --> 01:11:04.524
RACHEL:
She was here.

01:11:04.526 --> 01:11:06.627
DAVID:
It's okay.

01:11:06.995 --> 01:11:08.295
Mommy was here.

01:11:08.297 --> 01:11:09.429
